summary: A powerful enchantment for your weapons, it has the power to kill almost everything.
descriptionHtml:
God's Gift, Wield yourself with the power of god to smite those who oppose you!

This mod adds a weapon to the game called "God's Gift" which is just for disenchantment, and the second thing it adds is.. the enchantment!
It's a very powerful enchantment which has the power to kill almost anything, even at the lowest level!
author: uiuiass
